room_title: Escape room "Fallout Shelter" by 11th Hour Escape in Dallas-Fort Worth
room_description:
Are you there... over.  Please respond... over.
It's the end of the world. And you find yourself locked in a fallout shelter. There are plenty of supplies to last you and your group awhile. But that's where the good news ends. You discover a problem with the oxygen supply and realize you must escape the shelter in 60 minutes. Luckily, there are clues to help you make it out before you and your group are... over.
